# Pinned stock SDL3 for the SPIKE-3 / sim runtime harness (reproducibility anchor).
# STOCK upstream SDL3 — NOT libSDL3-pocketforge (the sunxifb fork). SPIKE-3 proves the
# INPUT/gamepad-enumeration layer, which is independent of SDL's video backend, so the
# GPU/sunxifb fork is irrelevant here (rendering honesty is tsp-an4.4). Built gamepad-only
# (no video/audio/udev/dbus/hidapi) and STATIC, so the arm64 probe runs under qemu-tsp with
# no sysroot.
repo = https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL.git
tag  = release-3.4.10
# Latest stable SDL3 at 2026-06-26. Even MINOR (3.2/3.4) = stable line.
